{"tid":1358470,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"除左丁權 大家還可以做呢樣！「內附詳細資訊」","createTime":"2019-07-24T02:38:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T07:27:25.000Z","uid":257401,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ec24c9a59e02eb37f883427f87b3f816a37e54e6","tid":1358470,"uid":257401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:38:52.000Z","msg":"除了丁權<br />\n係圍村好多村民的泊車位都係霸佔政府地<br />\n怎至已經僭建左頂蓋做有蓋車位<br />\n解決方法：<br />\n短線 -&gt; 可向1823投訴遺例泊車或克盡己任的警察部投訴<br />\n( <a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/contact_us.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2Fcontact_us.html&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1S2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=e083d2d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/contact_us.html</a> )<br />\n<br />\n長線 -&gt; 可向地政投訴霸佔官地或經1823轉介<br />\n<br />\n首先，可上 <a href=\"https://www.map.gov.hk/gm/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.map.gov.hk%2Fgm%2F&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1S2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=840398ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.map.gov.hk/gm/</a> 尋找各位市民有懷疑的地段（DD LOT）號碼，之後就可以用<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>google街景</strong></span>或者<strong>衛星圖片</strong>，睇下有無<strong>僭建物</strong>或者<strong>車輛</strong>，如果有就可以以附近地段編號（例如： DD123LOT1234 對出之政府路/政府官地）作定位[最好cap埋圖片]，再加埋google maps既經緯度會更好，以作投訴。<br />\n<br />\n地政處投訴熱線  22313369 （<a href=\"https://www.landsd.gov.hk/tc/about/enquiries.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.landsd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout%2Fenquiries.htm&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1S2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=fe917a9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.landsd.gov.hk/tc/about/enquiries.htm</a>）"},{"pid":"9f4de4963dc10b1bdf981797cb5b22da75b6a43f","tid":1358470,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:41:32.000Z","msg":"元朗手足有野講 727去唔去都入黎睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cd136739694206